content.html:
Well, I am proud to say that it finally happened! This past Tuesday evening, I proposed to Lacey, my girlfriend of over 6 years. I am so thankful to have been blessed with the opportunity to be with Lacey for the past 6 years, and I am really looking forward to spending the rest of my life with her as my wife.

Thanks to everyone who has sent on words of congratulation and encouragement!
